version_description:
- Buy iTunes Vouchers
- Optimisation and improvements to enhance customer experience

- Optimised for iOS 7
- Smaller and lighter, making your App faster
- View available offers from FNB, personalised to your needs
- Apply for new Cheque, Investment and Credit Accounts

- Optimised for iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus
- Improved navigation
- Smaller and lighter, making your App faster
- View available offers from FNB, personalised to your needs
- Apply for new Cheque, Investment and Credit Accounts
- Send once-off Global Payments & add/maintain recipients from your phone

You can now unlock your App with Fingerprint ID*
- Smart inContact lets you approve or report fraud on online transactions
- You can now verify your newly linked devices and browsers with the App
- Secure Chat to your Team of Bankers**
- FNB Watch App allows you to:
• View your accounts and transaction history
• Make Payments from history or using GeoPayments
• Buy Prepaid from history
• View your Vouchers and Coupons
• Make a Cardless Cash Withdrawals

* Supported on all devices with a Fingerprint sensor running IOS 9+
** Only available to Premier, Private Clients and Private Wealth

- 3D Touch options from the FNB App icon for iPhone 6S+ devices
- Authenticate card activations via Smart inContact via FNB Call Centres
- Minor improvements and fixes

- Prepaid Electricity updates: Receive your token on SMS and push message
- DSTV Prepaid in South Africa, Namibia, Swaziland, Zambia and Tanzania

- FNB TV: Watch FNB TV to catch up on the latest products and learn more about the FNB App.
- nav» Car: Manage your cars in one useful place, receive fine notifications and licence disc reminders.
- eBucks Partner Locator: Find an eBucks partner using augmented reality on the FNB App.
- Life Insurance: Apply for life cover; critical illness cover and disability cover.
- Messages (One Unified Look): Experience our new unified look on the Messages tab.
- Change your pin, temporarily block your card and request statements for Credit and Cheque accounts.
- Cardless cash Withdrawal functionality to registered Banking App clients in FNB Namibia, Botswana and Zambia.

We’ve improved our Product Shop – now opening accounts on the app is even easier with relevant information to help you make informed decisions. Just select Apply Here to try it out.

We’ve also made other small enhancements to improve your app experience.
